Package project4

Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • project4.Manager

  • public class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
    The Manager class implements the manager. It contains a constructor that initializes its providerRecords and memberRecords fields to the appropriate records it is passed. It also has two methods for printing the corresponding provider and member reports, as well as a terminal method that allows the manager to print these reports and a summary report, while generating a EFT file.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alan Manning
